  m_text: "\\u2022<indent=1em><b>Grid:</b> 10 \xD7 10 tiles. </indent>\n\\u2022<indent=1em><b>River:</b>
    The wavy tiles winding down the middle. You can't build on the river. </indent>\n\\u2022<indent=1em><b>Starting
    positions:</b> The 8 numbered spots. Your very first building must cover your
    chosen starting spot.</indent>"
