  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Each turn follows the same flow:


    <b>1.</b><indent=2em><b>Roll:</b>
    6 dice are rolled (3 Shape + 3 Building).</indent>

    <b>2.</b><indent=2em><b>Pick:</b>
    You choose 1 shape die + 1 building die.</indent>

    <b>3.</b><indent=2em><b>Position:</b>
    Tap the board, a shape appears. Drag it, rotate it, or flip it until it fits.</indent>

    <b>4.</b><indent=2em><b>Confirm:</b>
    Place it. If it''s green, you''re good; if red, it''s invalid.</indent>


    Repeat
    until you can no longer place a building.'
