  m_text: "The game ends automatically when you can't place the shapes in the dice
    pool anywhere on the board (and you have no wildcards left, or choose not to
    use one). \n\nIn multiplayer, when any player can't continue, the game ends for
    everyone.\n\nA scoreboard is shown with every player's final score. Click on
    one of the scores to see a full breakdown."
