  m_text: 'Stuck with bad dice? You get up to <b>3 wildcards</b> a game. A wildcard
    lets you pick any shape or building type freely, but they progressively cost
    more points per use:


    <b>\u2022</b><indent=2em><b>1st Use:</b> Costs 1 point</indent>

    <b>\u2022</b><indent=2em><b>2nd
    Use:</b> Costs 2 points</indent>

    <b>\u2022</b><indent=2em><b>3rd Use:</b>
    Costs 3 points</indent>


    <i>Press one of the wildcard buttons in the top
    panel</i>'
